[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13629] updated to latest reedline
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13625] added the osc633e escape for VS Code
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13613] created a better error message for bad glob patterns
, 
